## The Bottom-Up Forecasting Workflow

This methodology builds revenue forecasts from channel-level data up, using tiered attribution to properly credit each funnel stage.

```
Bottom-Up Forecast Workflow
в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ

Step 1: Historical Analysis
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Extract first-touch data (ToFU volume by channel)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Extract linear/participation data (MoFU engagement)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Extract last-touch data (BoFU conversions)
в””в”Җв”Җ Calculate stage conversion rates

Step 2: Funnel Flow Modeling
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Project ToFU leads by channel
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Apply ToFU вҶ’ MoFU conversion rate
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Apply MoFU вҶ’ BoFU conversion rate
в””в”Җв”Җ Apply channel overlap adjustment

Step 3: Revenue Calculation
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Multiply conversions Г— AOV
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Sum channel revenue for total
в””в”Җв”Җ Compare against historical actuals

Step 4: Validation & Adjustment
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Back-test against prior periods
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Adjust for seasonality
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Validate with incrementality data
в””в”Җв”Җ Document assumptions
```

## Step 1: Historical Analysis

### Extract Attribution Data by Stage

Pull data for each attribution model over a consistent time period (recommend 90+ days):

```sql
-- ToFU: First-touch by channel
SELECT
  first_touch_channel,
  COUNT(DISTINCT visitor_id) AS tofu_leads,
  DATE_TRUNC('month', first_touch_at) AS month
FROM journeys
WHERE first_touch_at >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '90 days'
GROUP BY first_touch_channel, DATE_TRUNC('month', first_touch_at);

-- MoFU: Linear credit by channel (engaged prospects)
SELECT
  channel,
  SUM(linear_credit) AS mofu_credit,
  COUNT(DISTINCT visitor_id) AS mofu_visitors
FROM mofu_touchpoints
WHERE touchpoint_at >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '90 days'
GROUP BY channel;

-- BoFU: Last-touch conversions and revenue
SELECT
  last_touch_channel,
  COUNT(*) AS conversions,
  SUM(revenue) AS revenue
FROM conversions
WHERE converted_at >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '90 days'
GROUP BY last_touch_channel;
```

### Calculate Stage Conversion Rates

For each channel, calculate how effectively it moves prospects through the funnel:

```
Stage Conversion Rate Formulas
в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ

ToFU вҶ’ MoFU Rate (per channel):
  = Visitors with channel in MoFU / Visitors with channel as first-touch
  = "Of the people this channel introduced, how many engaged further?"

MoFU вҶ’ BoFU Rate (per channel):
  = Conversions with channel in BoFU / Visitors with channel in MoFU
  = "Of the people this channel nurtured, how many converted?"

Overall Funnel Rate (per channel):
  = ToFUвҶ’MoFU Rate Г— MoFUвҶ’BoFU Rate
  = "End-to-end conversion rate for prospects from this channel"
```

